A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend an Act providing for the Heard County Board of Education, approved
2 March 28, 1985 (Ga. L. 1985, p. 5078), as amended, particularly by an Act approved May 3,
3 2018 (Ga. L. 2018, p. 3613), so as to revise the compensation of the members of the Heard
4 County Board of Education; to provide for related matters; to provide an effective date; to
5 repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 An Act providing for the Heard County Board of Education, approved March 28, 1985
9 (Ga. L. 1985, p. 5078), as amended, particularly by an Act approved May 3, 2018 (Ga. L.
10 2018, p. 3613), is amended by revising Section 6 as follows:
11 "SECTION 6.
12 Each member of the board shall receive $450.00 per month as compensation for his or her
13 services. While meeting or traveling outside Heard County as a member of the board, the
14 chairperson or any member of the board shall receive reimbursement for actual expenses
15 necessarily incurred in connection therewith. To be eligible for reimbursement, travel must
